➜本月超强打卡，美国潮牌Urban Outfitters空降魔都！
http://www.sohu.com/a/416388233_380622	9058
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/4b2b5dc740c241d9be93f2f2b34df0fb.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/c3a2f0cf5153445d815c83faf215d166.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
